# Portfolio Configuration
# Copy this to .env and update with your information

# Site Information
PORTFOLIO_NAME=Sure Profile
PORTFOLIO_TITLE=Full Stack Developer
PORTFOLIO_TAGLINE=Building beautiful and functional web experiences
PORTFOLIO_DESCRIPTION=A passionate developer crafting beautiful and functional web experiences

# Contact Information
